Kitabatakeshi shi jo-kan (Kitabatake clan`s residence and castle) was listed as one of the [[Continued Top 100 Japanese Castles]] in 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url= http://jokaku.jp/japan-top-100-castles/best-100-castles-of-japan-2nd-selection/ |title=続日本100名城 |publisher=日本城郭協会|language=Japanese|accessdate=25 July 2019}}</ref> [[File:Kiriyama Castle ruins.jpg|thumb|250px|Kiriyama Castle]]
